Staging: speakup: Use sizeof(*var) in kmalloc().

Modifying struct allocation in kmalloc() to match the
coding standards.

Checkpatch.pl CHECK: Prefer kmalloc(sizeof(*ldisc_data)...)
over kmalloc(sizeof(struct spk_ldisc_data)...)

